posting_body: ['San Francisco - Excelsior - House for rent', 'Charming 2 bedroom - 1 bath single family home', 'Link to mobile layout: \xa0 <URL>', 'Summary:', 'Rent: $3850', 'Bed / Bath: 2 / 1', 'Type: House', 'Term: 1 Year', 'Please contact:', 'Joanne Fazzino \xa0 |', 'show contact info', '| \xa0 \xa0 <URL>', 'Description:', 'You will love coming home to this charming 2 bedroom single family home in Mission Terrace.', 'Close to Glen Park BART and Balboa Park.', 'Set back off the street with front and back yards.', 'There is a garage and long driveway for plenty of parking.', 'Painted inside and out', 'Eat in kitchen with gas stove, dishwasher, refrigerator and disposal', 'Newer kitchen floor', 'Recently refinished hardwood floors in the living room and bedrooms', 'Decorative fireplace in the living room', '2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom', '4 Skylights and large windows bringing in lots of light', 'Washer and dryer provided in the garage', 'Lots of storage', 'Available now.', 'A pet will be considered.', 'This is a non-smoking unit.', 'Service or support animals which are necessary due to disability will be allowed.', 'Details:', 'Floors: Hardwood', 'Kitchen: Upgraded', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Outside area: Yard', 'Parking: Garage', 'Parking Fee: $0', 'Pets:  Negotiable', 'View: Street', 'Location:', 'Theresa Street & Cayuga Avenue, San Francisco, California', 'Meet the J.Wavro Team:', '<URL>', 'Please contact:', 'Joanne Fazzino \xa0 |', 'show contact info', '| \xa0 \xa0 <URL>', 'Preview more properties at <URL>', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.', 'Content and Images © 2003 - 2021 J.Wavro \xa0 | \xa0 BRE # 01810008 \xa0 | \xa0 cl31115292012072-0']
